deck: Reprints classic Rogue Trooper stories from 2000 AD.
description:
Eight issue mini-series.

Planned to be a 12-issue limited series it was cut short due to poor sales. The eight issues collect all the Rogue Trooper stories from the British weekly anthology title 2000 AD (1977), with added colors, between Rogue Trooper's very first story in Prog 228 and The Assassination Run arc in Progs 278-279. The original stories were published between 1981 and 1982.

Collected in Rogue Trooper Classics.
name: Rogue Trooper Classics
